presenter

Class Properties

  • java.lang.Object
    • presenter.Properties

  • public class Properties
extends java.lang.Object

    Properties

    Serializable class. Allows setting and getting of all properties needed. On init program, load an xml file into a Properties object from which we get data program needs.
    Author:
    Valentina Munoz & Moris Amon
